[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    1214[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;101;115;126m<!--[38;2;101;115;126m TODO (TechWriter): benchmark ranges are directional from typical patient-privacy-monitoring program performance. Specific figures vary substantially by health system size, EHR vendor, workforce composition, base rate of policy violations, and privacy office staffing. The published academic literature on healthcare insider threat detection is sparse compared with the operational literature; vendor-published metrics from Protenus, Imprivata FairWarning, and similar products provide additional reference points. Replace with measured numbers from local validation. [38;2;101;115;126m-->[K
